# 🎓 Campus Companion – Smart College Assistant 🚀

> A full-stack intelligent platform for students to manage timetables, placement drives, events, announcements, resources, and more — now accessible via Web and WhatsApp Assistant!

![Tech](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tech-FullStack-green)
![Built with](https://img.shields.io/badge/Stack-MERN-blue)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-v1.0.0-purple)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow)
![Open Source](https://badgen.net/badge/Open/Source/green)

---

## ✨ Features

- 📅 Personalized Timetable Viewer
- 📢 Real-time Announcements & Class Alerts
- 🎉 Upcoming Events & Fest Calendar
- 🧭 Interactive Campus Map (Room/Lab Search)
- 🧠 AI-powered AskBot for Student Queries
- 💼 Placement Drive Tracker + Eligibility Filters
- 📚 Notes, PYQs & Study Material Vault
- 🔔 WhatsApp Assistant Bot Integration *(Beta)*
- 🛠 Admin & CR Panel (Role-based)
- 🌐 Multilingual Support *(Hindi, Telugu, English)*
- 🎨 Modern Responsive UI with Dark Mode

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer       | Technology                            |
|-------------|----------------------------------------|
| Frontend    | React.js, TailwindCSS, Framer Motion   |
| Backend     | Node.js, Express.js                    |
| Database    | MongoDB + Mongoose                     |
| Auth        | Firebase Auth / JWT (Optional)         |
| Bot Layer   | Twilio / Meta WhatsApp API             |
| Hosting     | Vercel (Frontend), Railway (Backend)   |

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```

CampusCompanion/
├── client/         # React Frontend
├── server/         # Express Backend
├── bot/            # WhatsApp Bot Scripts
├── .env            # Environment Variables
└── README.md       # This file

````

---

## ⚙️ APIs Overview

| Endpoint               | Method | Purpose                             |
|------------------------|--------|-------------------------------------|
| `/api/timetable/:id`   | GET    | Fetch student timetable             |
| `/api/events`          | GET    | View upcoming college events        |
| `/api/notices`         | GET    | Get latest announcements            |
| `/api/placements`      | GET    | Placement drive info                |
| `/api/ask`             | POST   | Query the Campus AskBot             |
| `/api/resources/:sem`  | GET    | Notes & materials by semester       |

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/campus-companion.git
cd campus-companion
````

### 2️⃣ Set Up the Backend

```bash
cd server
npm install
npm run dev
```

### 3️⃣ Set Up the Frontend

```bash
cd ../client
npm install
npm start
```

### 4️⃣ (Optional) Start Bot Tunnel

```bash
cd ../bot
node webhook.js
```

---

## 📱 WhatsApp Bot Demo (Optional)

> Powered by Twilio or Meta Business API
> Allows voice/text queries like:
>
> * “What’s today’s class?”
> * “Where is CS301 class?”
> * “Upcoming hackathon?”

---

## 🧠 AI AskBot Dataset Sample

```json
{
  "When is the next fest?": "The next fest is Innovatia on Aug 5.",
  "Where is ECE Block?": "It’s behind the Admin building, 2nd left from the main gate.",
  "Who is the CR of 3rd year CSE?": "That’s Ankit Verma."
}
```

---

## 🛡️ Admin Panel

| Role    | Access Level                         |
| ------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Admin   | Full CRUD on events, drives, notices |
| CR      | Can post announcements only          |
| Student | Read-only access to all modules      |

